{"tid":587010,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【極罕見】兩樹熊為求偶大打出手　澳洲荒野上演摔角大戰","createTime":"2018-03-10T05:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T06:41:29.000Z","uid":109136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a3420d8c2e31f76cb41c18b5959fdef437b755","tid":587010,"uid":109136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/166737/thumbnail/cdafc5258b713e81ffda6d54b977ccab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F166737%2Fthumbnail%2Fcdafc5258b713e81ffda6d54b977ccab.jpg&h=1ffffe66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提起樹熊，除了口中含着尤加利葉那頭樹熊，絕大部分樹熊的形象都是可愛又溫順，但牠們都有大打出手的時候，看來是為了女人。近日，一名澳洲男子拍到兩頭樹熊為了求偶大打出手，雙方合演摔角大戰互有攻守，最後其中一隻敗走收場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1264651/xlarge/f251bd752d918f5dba011d7dcf2aca12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1264651%2Fxlarge%2Ff251bd752d918f5dba011d7dcf2aca12.jpg&h=1f09850e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩隻雄性樹熊為了求偶大打出手。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居於南澳洲南部郊區貝萊爾（Belair）的麥士維（Bennett Maxwell），將拍到的樹熊打鬥片上載至網絡。片段開始時兩隻樹熊扭作一團，其中一隻樹熊用手和頭將另一隻壓倒地上。倒地樹熊腰間發力，手腳並用將對方推開。被推開的樹熊見對手尚未調整好，馬上出爪抓實敵方頭部，再用頭部嘗試將對手壓在地上。可惜處於下方的樹熊穩住陣勢，雙手撐地發力擺脫，兩熊面貼面對峙，儼如兩名摔角手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二回合開打，之前處於劣勢的樹熊搶佔先機，出拳攻擊對方頭部。豈料對方側面閃避，順勢用手將牠按倒地上。本以為大局已定，但處於劣勢的樹熊並未放棄，倒地前轉身攻擊對手腰側，反手一掌打落對方腰間，乘勢按牠背部壓倒對方。原本一直佔優的樹熊見勢色不對，轉身就跑，劣勢樹熊得勢不饒人，從後追趕對方。這場大戰告訴我們，比賽一日未完，大家千萬不要放棄。<br />\n<br />\n麥士維表示，鏡頭外有一隻雌性樹熊觀戰，相信兩隻雄性樹熊是為了求偶大打出手。一般來說，樹熊只為爭地盤打鬥，很少因「感情事」出手。據澳洲無尾熊基金會（ Australian Koala Foundation）的資料，樹熊繁殖季節在每年8月至2月。<br />\n<br />\n（每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/166737/-%E6%A5%B5%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B-%E5%85%A9%E6%A8%B9%E7%86%8A%E7%82%BA%E6%B1%82%E5%81%B6%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%93%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%8D%92%E9%87%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%94%E6%91%94%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F166737%2F-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E7%25BD%2595%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E7%2586%258A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2581%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2589%258B-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%258D%2592%25E9%2587%258E%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%2591%2594%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B0&d=UxkIpY85DJFtukfYwSSGUBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fd9f8032\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/166737/-%E6%A5%B5%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B-%E5%85%A9%E6%A8%B9%E7%86%8A%E7%82%BA%E6%B1%82%E5%81%B6%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%93%E5%87%BA%E6%89%8B-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%8D%92%E9%87%8E%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%94%E6%91%94%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0</a>"},{"pid":"64ca8e9a8e7ef0add67298d4251454d411a9de4a","tid":587010,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"koala' 太靚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acff51ad5af33c8584c86530254616a138a87fe9","tid":587010,"uid":8171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f4/MnVy1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20121107040136\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff4%2FMnVy1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20121107040136&h=3c8662c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/b12818NiUqQp5a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fb12818NiUqQp5a34.jpg&h=33379082&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25f7cdab7c0e7102e9d9eeb8e83df6b71e3d6140","tid":587010,"uid":39582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"屌閪真係生物活著既動力<br />\n連登仔唔撚明架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcc83e5816c19b0201fc673b30bac8d0f80d076","tid":587010,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c7059cd1a5a76883e04bb310072f15f88db4eb","tid":587010,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"尤加利葉背摔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5b7606a2232c872c93c92ffc735bdd2de57130","tid":587010,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"有閪屌唯有現真身"}]}